<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="a19Jul1933"><font color="red">19 July 1933</font> <i>NLPL</i> (to Paul L&eacute;on): We return probably to Paris on Sunday (23 July 1933) &hellip; prof. Fehr &hellip; has not received the pamphlet <i>Das Wort</i> by Rudolf Leonard (the man who was helping to translate A.L.P. into German with Goyert) </div>
